{"tid":1398430,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"8月4號區外人夜遊將軍澳係自殺行為！！！","createTime":"2019-08-02T19:37:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T06:13:41.000Z","uid":44201,"like":104,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"630b186596c553a9fee2b349317cc4d7b6d660b8","tid":1398430,"uid":44201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T19:37:12.000Z","msg":"身為將軍澳人，有責任要提大家將軍澳係一個易入難出嘅口袋形盤地，只要封死曬三條路+停狗鐵服務，發完夢想起身嘅人係唔會醒到<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1.將軍澳隧道</span><br />\n就算隧道口冇roadblock，所有唔係直上觀塘繞道嘅車都會經過觀塘警署，但係觀塘繞道本身就係「飛車黑點」，狗狗好鐘意玩追車嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2.寶琳北路往秀茂坪</span><br />\n寶琳路一出秀茂坪就會經過秀茂坪警署，後果係點自己諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">3.清水灣道</span><br />\n條路係可以經西貢出沙田、馬鞍山一帶，亦可以去科大，但同樣道理，狗可以喺路頭路尾路中放rb<br />\n中途轉出去經壁屋監獄出佐敦谷又會經過順利警察宿舍，又冇得行<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">4.澳景路</span><br />\n唔使諗喇，私家路，晨早就俾維景灣畔封咗，<span style=\"color: red;\">分分鐘俾狗用嚟從後包抄</span><br />\n<br />\n溫馨提示：<br />\n唔好以為入村食宵夜好安全，將軍澳好多白衫嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你以為行山路就避到？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你試下夜晚行個幾鐘山路吖，地勢陰險，碌咗落山都冇人知呀</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呼籲大家行完個遊行就好返去自己嗰區，或者參加另一個有不反對通知書嘅集會，做個守法公民呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cbc1aa4e0c9a1298d1ca21de5359127951f07d5","tid":1398430,"uid":203889,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T19:45:02.000Z","msg":"同意<br />\n果邊好麻煩<br />\n<br />\n假文宣都話要塞三隧！各位小心！！<br />\n<br />\n義士有生命危險！！8月5號有危險，快入！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1392370\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1392370</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>第11頁有藍絲假文宣合集</strong></span><br />\n補番真文宣source<br />\n5/8 全港大三罷+ 7區開🌼 公海<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/saveinghkgrp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fsaveinghkgrp&d=JkVIzhDRZadGdMc0KemjDXXW3JPDzH8o%2FFP8rJ6jlcg%3D&h=238ad3a0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/saveinghkgrp</a>"},{"pid":"a5fd6b0593575026af3f11ffcde741de3b88a4a6","tid":1398430,"uid":49979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T19:46:20.000Z","msg":"詳盡分析<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93437843f187d15f93171ff2450466722b02f140","tid":1398430,"uid":44201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T19:53:43.000Z","msg":"推！真係困獸鬥嫁！"},{"pid":"e8a9353e436b50e43ce3019cfe364ccfeecf06ee","tid":1398430,"uid":258377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T20:11:01.000Z","msg":"我估好多人會去港島，本住人越多越安全嘅大原則，我會去將軍澳<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3553d75312fe0fbc8d270c19bb998315fc330514","tid":1398430,"uid":29153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T20:12:34.000Z","msg":"咁順灘，和理非去吧"},{"pid":"b65383405ea4a14e1486ea12519f92f859ffe6d8","tid":1398430,"uid":110969,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T20:30:07.000Z","msg":"大把屋苑大堂入啦，我第一個hold 住對門救各位巴打<br />\n利申將軍澳撚"},{"pid":"8a73b0610793e4780c68ab81c58576110a043356","tid":1398430,"uid":31788,"like":0,"dislike":18,"score":-18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T22:10:21.000Z","msg":"今日收到風班數字頭黑社會收咗錢入嚟搞事<br />\n但將軍澳好似大部分都係新字頭<br />\n不排除嗰日將會有黑吃黑事件"},{"pid":"8328c819bc118cd22d1e6307f2a89a4983791480","tid":1398430,"uid":294230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T23:00:33.000Z","msg":"夜晚我應該已經去咗西區"},{"pid":"0436fb80811f564e645ac739dc02cfb12201a5e9","tid":1398430,"uid":164372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"93437843f187d15f93171ff2450466722b02f140","tid":1398430,"uid":44201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"201