es/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dnTM3NV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdnTM3NV.png&h=6d3b446e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5dbc81002de1e22a8700f19dad13416c1fedc258","tid":1398430,"uid":40932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T01:55:42.000Z","msg":"再險既元朗都去過<br />\n會驚山路？"},{"pid":"86becb770561bc5526d18ed4f8b06c81e1bac40b","tid":1398430,"uid":240608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T01:58:27.000Z","msg":"經油塘過海啦 最撚安全"},{"pid":"9756f07452bacedb9cf0ee4b30315af62d96d58d","tid":1398430,"uid":109712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5dbc81002de1e22a8700f19dad13416c1fedc258","tid":1398430,"uid":40932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T01:55:42.000Z","msg":"再險既元朗都去過<br />\n會驚山路？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T02:00:22.000Z","msg":"元朗的險係內部險，但散可以行去天水圍，搭車都有天水圍/屯門、錦上路、上水幾個唔同方向。將軍澳得一鐵一隧"},{"pid":"bc658366390fbb5d729c888a6da8278569c1c21c","tid":1398430,"uid":209531,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T02:11:45.000Z","msg":"同意，唔好次次遊行都留守，反正8月都仲有幾次遊行，搵啲地勢對大家有利嘅地區先做，或者玩快閃都得。最緊要唔好白白送頭，記得運動最初可以成功係靠大家一句「Be water, my friends. 」。"},{"pid":"91a6338c66d8115f5bc9410423eb90cdd1925a4c","tid":1398430,"uid":17619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T02:23:37.000Z","msg":"黎我屋企"},{"pid":"a2571cfd0dbf27c5fa15af34ebfef10af0dce3d7","tid":1398430,"uid":44201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5dbc81002de1e22a8700f19dad13416c1fedc258","tid":1398430,"uid":40932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T01:55:42.000Z","msg":"再險既元朗都去過<br />\n會驚山路？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T02:25:03.000Z","msg":"體力問題"},{"pid":"b5af0efa2085a75e9f0d700df45b4ea85e036d43","tid":1398430,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T02:28:28.000Z","msg":"走唔到就留下先,太急走反而未必好"}]}